PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (TA'AN KWACH'AN COUNCIL, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of specified tracts of land in the Yukon Territory until April 1, 2007, and (b) repeals a similar Order enacted by Order in Council P.C. 2001-2298 of December 13, 2001.
